  <text>
    <body>
      <div subtype="original" type="letter" xml:id="L.2073" xml:lang="de">
        <pb facs="#IMG.1" n="1"/>
        <dateline>[Stempel: Privatdozent Dr.Spitzer Pörtschach a.See Kärnten Villa Leonstein]</dateline>
        <p>fragt, was Sie zu folgenden Etymologien sagen: <ref
            target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.779">sp</ref>. <foreign xml:lang="es">
            <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">mandria</hi>
          </foreign> 'Faulpelz, Faulheit', <ref
            target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.864">
kat</ref>. <foreign xml:lang="ca">
            <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
mandra</hi>
          </foreign> = aprov. <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
mandra</hi> 'weiblicher Fuchs' (cf. aprov. <hi
            rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
volpilh</hi> 'feige')</p>
        <p>
          <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.779">sp</ref>. <foreign xml:lang="es">
            <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">gurrumina</hi>
          </foreign> 'Pantoffelheldentum' = *<hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">worm</hi> 'Eiter' (<ref
            target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.779">sp</ref>. <foreign xml:lang="es">
            <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">gormar</hi>
          </foreign> 'erbrechen'), <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">-ina</hi> wie in <hi rend="unknown"
            rendition="#none">hedentina</hi>, <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">gurrum-</hi> = <hi rend="unknown"
            rendition="#none">gurm-</hi> wie in <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">gurumete</hi>, <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">gurupa</hi>, zur Bdtg. die amerik.-sp. Bdtgen. 'enclen que, chiquitin', persona lista y astuta? </p>
        <pb facs="#IMG.2" n="2"/>
        <p>
          <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.779">Sp</ref>.<ref
            target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.844">Ptg</ref>. <hi rend="unknown"
            rendition="#none">garduño</hi> 'Marder' = <ref
            target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.844">ptg</ref>. <foreign xml:lang="pt">
            <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">gadunha</hi>
          </foreign>, <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.779">sp</ref>. <foreign xml:lang="es">
            <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">guadaña</hi>
          </foreign> 'Pickel, Kralle' (galiz. <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">garridunha</hi> unter Einfluß von <hi
            rend="unknown" rendition="#none">garrido</hi>, die -r-Formen von <hi rend="unknown"
            rendition="#none">garfa</hi>, <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
garra</hi> her).</p>
        <p>Haben Sie über <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">garduño</hi> nicht etwas geäußert?</p>
        <closer>
          <salute>Herzlichst </salute>
          <signed>
            <persName ref="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.persons#P.877">Spitzer</persName>
          </signed>
        </closer>
      </div>
